Do you have a background in BI or DW development, data analysis/science, database development, or Big Data development?  Do you have an interest in emerging Big Data technologies, Advanced Analytics or cloud-native data warehouse technologies? 
              If so, read on, as this consulting business has work that will be of interest to you!As a Data Engineering Consultant, you will be involved in a breadth of technologies and environments, and so this role will expand your skills and
              experience.  You will work with exceptionally talented engineers, bringing innovative and technically advanced solutions to your clients.  Your work will see you constantly working with the latest technology, tools and concepts,
              particularly in data and analytics, Big Data and Cloud technologies.  Candidates who would be suited to this role might come from one or several of the below technology/experience groups:

Strong experience with SQL and various database technologies;
Development experience in languages such as Python, Scala, Java, TSQL, PL/SQL etc. or other would be of interest;
Experience with Big Data or an interest in the following technologies:  Spark, Kafka, Hive, Airflow, NiFi;
Experience building end to end data pipelines using both on-premise or cloud based data platforms;
Cloud-native data platform exposure, such as BigQuery, Redshift, Snowflake, Azure DW;
Those with experience in AWS, Google Cloud or Azure will be of high interest.
 As you can see, this role allows for candidates from a range of specialisations or disciplines, as there are several lines of specialisation within this consulting business.  As they are in a high growth phase now, getting in early
              will allow for the greatest opportunities to pursue your areas of interest.  Some additional benefits for working with this business include a strong commitment to investing in training and sponsoring certifications, career
              development and the work itself will keep you interested due to the variety of project work.  Apply today online or call Riki on 0433168509.

